{"tid":1817000,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"涉去年10月九龍塘站掟汽油彈　5名男子被捕","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T17:47:05.000Z","uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da16c60f4801cc32b37b0d4c813b51e934800d41","tid":1817000,"uid":153956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-08-2020/58896\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F01-08-2020%2F58896&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF03aXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=3e1fc899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/01-08-2020/58896</a><br />\n<br />\n警方以涉嫌串謀縱火拘捕5名男子，懷疑他們與去年10月12日向港鐵九龍塘站出口投擲汽油彈有關。  警方表示5人互相認識，年齡介乎26至40歲，相信其中兩人負責投擲汽油彈，另外2人負責開車接走疑犯逃走。至於另一名26歲男子，警方在他住所搜出5支汽油彈、2支氣槍、1支胡椒噴霧、2把軍刀、7個防毒面罩，以及一些懷疑可以製造易燃物品的材料。  警方指5人無被捕紀錄，但部分人有參與近期的示威活動。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4465a384a29646b6515ec0f63509fd15ae859c","tid":1817000,"uid":198590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#153956 - 千萬窮能</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>係時候諗定輸左後點做 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>唔係講笑各位連青人, 係時候諗定, 日日9叫唱歌既革命輸得7788, 準備比人上門清算<br />\n<br />\n1,2,3,4定10年, 寫定張平安紙交帶</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1687659/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>睇你地班人既所謂革命 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>黎黎去去係街9 叫<br />\n<br />\n見警就縮<br />\n<br />\n咁攪法攪到幾時先成功？留比你地個孫接手曱命？<br />\n<br />\n初初都好笑消閒下時間，可惜越睇越悶</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1685603/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1685603/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<